 What is the value of IDB? - It can be calculated by valuing the (weighted)
 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

portfolio
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 of its holdings.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
On top of that, specific off balance sheet items must be added.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The value of a collection of assets can be different from the value of the
 holding company (
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

the holding company puzzle
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

) - as the market also prices the 
\series bold
PV of other activities
\series default
 in the firm, for example:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
